* [[Australian of the Year|Honorary Australian of the Year]] in the UK, 26 January 2014<ref>{{cite news |title=London mayor Boris Johnson named honorary Australian of the Year |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jan/26/boris-johnson-honorary-australian-year |agency=Associated Press |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=26 January 2014 |access-date=6 October 2019 |archive-date=30 September 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930025351/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jan/26/boris-johnson-honorary-australian-year |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Magnay 2014">{{cite web |last=Magnay |first=Jacquelin |title=Boris Johnson admits to being a bit baffled by honorary Aussie award |url=https://www.theaustralian.com.au/in-depth/australia-day/boris-johnson-admits-to-being-a-bit-baffled-by-honorary-aussie-award/news-story/60f536e52671675d38466e899b7afdc9 |website=The Australian |access-date=26 August 2020 |date=26 January 2014}}</ref>
