* Medical Education [[Ig Nobel Prize]], 2020.<ref>{{cite journal |last=Tanne |first=Janice Hopkins |date=18 September 2020 |title=Donald Trump, Boris Johnson, and other leaders win Ig Nobel awards for teaching people about life and death |url=https://www.bmj.com/content/370/bmj.m3675 |journal=BMJ |volume=370 |pages=m3675 |doi=10.1136/bmj.m3675 |issn=1756-1833 |pmid=32948527 |s2cid=221766743 |access-date=30 July 2022 |archive-date=29 September 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929101002/https://www.bmj.com/content/370/bmj.m3675 |url-status=live}}</ref>
